aiConfig.userPromptTemplate:
Generate {{count}} realistic and commonly-used options for a "{{displayName}}" dropdown list.

Context Information:
- List Type: {{displayName}}
- Category: {{category}}
- Description: {{description}}
- Internal Name: {{name}}
- Sort Preference: {{sortBy}}
- Allows Custom Values: {{allowCustom}}

{{#userPrompt}}Additional Requirements: {{userPrompt}}

{{/userPrompt}}Instructions:
- Generate practical, real-world options that users would commonly need
- Each option should have a clear, user-friendly label
- Values must be unique, URL-safe (lowercase, no spaces, use hyphens/underscores)
- Include brief descriptions that explain when to use each option
- Consider the category "{{category}}" when generating options
- Make options relevant to business/enterprise applications
- Ensure consistent formatting and naming conventions

Return a JSON object with this exact structure:
{
  "options": [
    {
      "label": "Display Name",
      "value": "unique_value",
      "description": "Brief explanation of when to use this option"
    }
  ]
}

Requirements:
- Return only valid JSON, no additional text or formatting
- Ensure all values are unique within the list
- Labels should be professional and clear
- Descriptions should be concise but informative
- CRITICAL: Your response must be valid JSON that starts with { and ends with }
